---
title: Beefy Nachos! with Beans and Tomato Salsa
description: Whether you’re entertaining or having a cosy night in, our homemade cheesy nachos with a meaty bean chilli and tomato salsa are the ultimate crowd-pleasing recipe. For the nachos themselves, the best flavour can be produced simply by cutting whole wheat tortillas into triangles and baking until brown and crispy. It’s really worth the extra effort for chips that don’t got soggy under the toppings! Plate everything up in the middle of your table and tuck in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-nachos-ea7753bb-dc974e58.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/cheesy-nachos-5bc07f4230006c2b844bf972-ccd0b680.pdf
